data.clean_description: On offer we have pharmaceutical grade seroquel 300 mg tablets. Seroquel is a anti-psychotic which is widely used in the treatment of individuals suffering mental illnesses such as bi-polar and schizophrenia or in the rare case fellow partying people as the best way to combat those dreadful comedowns. Once you try one of these puppies , you will never have to reach for a benzo again. We recommend you take half a tablet and wait 30 minutes before dropping the other half approximately 1hr before you intend on being asleep if you have nt had any experience with the dosage size.
data.name: Seroquel 300mg - **STOPS TRIPS**- 5 tablets
